s by a great deliverance.","year":-1707},{"id":"rectcpK5m75QkB9cx","ref":"Gen.45.8","text":"So now it was not you that sent me hither, but God: and he hath made me a father to Pharaoh, and lord of all his house, and a ruler throughout all the land of Egypt.","year":-1707}]}
